# VHS Script: VSCode Integration Demo
# Shows how ccu runs in VSCode's integrated terminal

Output ../images/01-usage-mode.gif

# Terminal settings
Set FontSize 37
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 0.05s
Set Padding 10 


Hide

# Start the program
Type "ccu"
Enter
Sleep 15s

Show 

# Switch views
Tab
Sleep 3s

# Switch views
Tab
Sleep 3s

# Switch views
Tab
Sleep 2s

# Switch views
Tab
Sleep 2s
